OL,3,CFears of 'medical emergency' as
OL,4,CDelhi's toxic air crisis worsens
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer, Sanjay Jha
OL,8,FNew Delhi is facing one of its gravest
OL,9,Fenvironmental and public-health
OL,10,Fcatastrophes in years, with senior
OL,11,Fdoctors at the country's premier
OL,12,Fhospital, the All India Institute of
OL,13,FMedical Sciences (AIIMS), warning that
OL,14,Fthe capital's air has deteriorated to
OL,15,F"medical emergency" levels.
OL,17,FThey say the surge in pollution is
OL,18,Faffecting people across all age
OL,19,Fgroups, from unborn children to the
OL,20,Felderly.
