OL,3,CFears of 'medical emergency' as
OL,4,CDelhi's toxic air crisis worsens
OL,6,FDr Anant Mohan, head of pulmonary
OL,7,Fmedicine at AIIMS, said Delhi's toxic
OL,8,Fair is now a multisystem threat.
OL,10,F"We have definite evidence that long-
OL,11,Fterm exposure cuts life expectancy and
OL,12,Fincreases mortality," he warned.
OL,14,FHe added that the damage begins "long
OL,15,Fbefore birth".
OL,17,FSince the Diwali festival earlier this
OL,18,Fmonth, hospital departments across the
OL,19,Fcity have reported a 10`15% rise in
OL,20,Frespiratory illnesses.
