OL,3,CFears of 'medical emergency' as
OL,4,CDelhi's toxic air crisis worsens
OL,6,FA&Es and clinics are crowded with
OL,7,Fpatients complaining of persistent
OL,8,Fcough, breathlessness, wheezing and
OL,9,Feye irritation ` including many who
OL,10,Fhave never experienced such symptoms
OL,11,Fbefore.
OL,13,FDoctors say personal measures like
OL,14,Fmasks and air purifiers offer only
OL,15,Flimited protection.
OL,17,F"Temporary fixes won't save us," Dr
OL,18,FMohan said.
