OL,3,CFears of 'medical emergency' as
OL,4,CDelhi's toxic air crisis worsens
OL,6,F"The city needs sustained, year-round
OL,7,Finterventions, not short bursts of
OL,8,Faction in November."
OL,10,FEach winter, stagnant winds, low
OL,11,Ftemperatures, and a temperature-
OL,12,Finversion effect trap pollutants close
OL,13,Fto the ground, creating a dense smog
OL,14,Fblanket that can last for weeks.
OL,16,FThis often leads to the closure of
OL,17,Fschools and a switch to online classes.
