OL,3,CFears of 'medical emergency' as
OL,4,CDelhi's toxic air crisis worsens
OL,6,FAs conditions worsen, residents have
OL,7,Ftaken to the streets in protest.
OL,8,FHundreds of students, activists, and
OL,9,Ffamilies gathered at Delhi's Jantar
OL,10,FMantar, demanding clean air and
OL,11,Faccountability.
OL,13,FProtesters held placards reading "Let
OL,14,FDelhi Breathe" and "Declare Climate
OL,15,FEmergency," accusing authorities of
OL,16,Fyears of inaction.
OL,18,FParticipants described headaches,
OL,19,Fnausea, and difficulty breathing; many
OL,20,Fnow avoid outdoor activity entirely.
