OL,3,CFears of 'medical emergency' as
OL,4,CDelhi's toxic air crisis worsens
OL,6,FThey also pointed out that the crisis
OL,7,Fextends beyond Delhi; neighbouring
OL,8,Fcities in Uttar Pradesh, Haryana,
OL,9,FPunjab, and Rajasthan are battling
OL,10,Fsimilarly hazardous air.
OL,12,FLast month, the Indian government
OL,13,Fattempted to address the problem of
OL,14,Fpollution in New Delhi with an
OL,15,Fartificial cloud seeding operation.
