OL,3,CFears of 'medical emergency' as
OL,4,CDelhi's toxic air crisis worsens
OL,6,FThe process, a collaboration with the
OL,7,FIndian Institute of Technology (IIT)
OL,8,FKanpur, involved spraying substances
OL,9,Fsuch as silver iodide into clouds in
OL,10,Fan attempt to trigger rain and wash
OL,11,Fpollutants out of the air.
OL,13,FIts efforts were considered largely
OL,14,Funsuccessful on account of the low
OL,15,Fmoisture content in the atmosphere,
OL,16,Fwith the small decrease in air
OL,17,Fpollution being attributed to natural
OL,18,Fweather patterns.
