OL,11,FThe toxic air has driven a sharp rise
OL,12,Fin air-purifier sales across Delhi-
OL,13,FNCR, transforming what was once a
OL,14,Fniche, seasonal product into a booming
OL,15,Fyear-round business.
OL,17,FResearch firm Markets & Data projects
OL,18,Fthe sector could grow more than 12%
OL,19,Fannually till 2033, fuelled by
OL,20,Fworsening pollution and growing public
OL,21,Fanxiety about health.
