OL,4,CDelhi's toxic air crisis worsens
OL,6,FFor companies, Delhi's air-quality
OL,7,Fdisaster has become a lucrative
OL,8,Fbusiness moment ` one that expands
OL,9,Fsharply each time the city's pollution
OL,10,Flevels plunge into the "severe" zone.
OL,12,FMarketing campaigns now highlight the
OL,13,Fdanger of "invisible indoor
OL,14,Fpollutants," urging consumers to look
OL,15,Fbeyond outdoor smog and focus on the
OL,16,Fair inside their homes ` a shift many
OL,17,Fresidents see as tapping into fear
OL,18,Fcreated by the crisis.
