OL,6,FManufacturers increasingly release new
OL,7,Fmodels timed to coincide with the
OL,8,Fwinter pollution spike, promoting
OL,9,Ffeatures such as ultrafine particle
OL,10,Ffiltration, whole-room circulation,
OL,11,Fand app-based air-quality monitoring.
OL,13,FSeveral brands have also introduced
OL,14,Fdiscounts, exchange schemes, and
OL,15,Ftargeted digital ads aimed at urban
OL,16,Ffamilies, young professionals, and
OL,17,Feven schools.
